<a href="/questions/417154-can-i-read-this-as-a-stand-alone-book-or">Can I read this as a stand alone book or should I read the earlier books in the series first?</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_417154'><a id="like_count_community_question_417154" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/417154?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F408855.Wizard_and_Glass">like</a></span>

