        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer683655815" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15487136785477572116"><b>(A-) 84%</b> | Very Good<br/><i>Notes:</i> A slow, but never dull, build to a thrilling climax, it provides the sorely needed back-story lacking in previous books.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

